## 19. Performance Requirements

Performance matters especially for global and Haiti-based audiences.

### Requirements

* fast page loads
* optimized images
* lightweight frontend behavior
* graceful handling on slower internet
* minimal blocking scripts
* good Core Web Vitals targets

### Product Standard

The website should feel fast enough that users do not bounce before the content loads.

---

## 20. Trust and Credibility Features

EdLight News needs visible signals of editorial seriousness.

### Recommended Trust Features

* About page explaining mission
* Editorial standards page
* clear attribution on articles
* correction/update handling if needed
* publication dates visible
* source transparency where appropriate
* clean, typo-free presentation

### Why This Matters

Without visible trust signals, the site may feel like an amateur content project even if the content itself is strong.

