## 21. Social and Ecosystem Integration

The site should connect well with EdLight’s broader ecosystem.

### Integration Goals

* capture traffic coming from Instagram
* create pathways to EdLight programs where relevant
* reinforce EdLight’s mission without making the news site feel promotional

### Possible Integrations

* links to EdLight main website
* links to EdLight Code, Academy, or ESLP when contextually relevant
* embedded social follow prompts
* promotional modules used sparingly

The site should still stand on its own as a media product.

