## 27. Final Product Requirement Statement

The EdLight News website must be a premium, fast, mobile-first digital publication that combines credible news, useful opportunities, and strong editorial design for Haitian youth, the diaspora, and globally minded readers. It should feel modern, trustworthy, and purposeful, with clear structure, strong discovery, and an identity strong enough to stand as a flagship EdLight media product.
